# Parachute Trains Puzzle

This is a Next.js web application that visually simulates the "parachute trains on a railway line" puzzle. 
Two trains on an infinite railway must find each other using identical algorithms without communication.

## Tech Stack

- **Framework**: Next.js 16 (App Router)
- **UI**: React 19
- **Animations**: Framer Motion
- **Icons**: Lucide React
- **Styling**: Plain CSS (no Tailwind)
- **Language**: TypeScript

## File Structure Convention

```
app/           # Next.js App Router pages and layouts
components/    # Reusable React components
hooks/         # Custom React hooks (if needed)
lib/           # Utility functions (if needed)
public/        # Static assets
```
